 he gets up and starts after jane 
 lesteryou treat us both like employees 
 carolyn looks after him 
 int burnham house continuous 
 a huge faux industrial kitchen with whiteceramic tile brushed steel appliances and antique hardware and lighting this is one of those designer kitchens that cost a fortune jane stands at the sink rinsing off her plate lester enters 
